I was just looking at the new V3 API but how can I filter on last modified deals? Using the following filter doesn’t seem to work:

```{
    "filters": [
        {
            "propertyName": "hs_lastmodifieddate",
            "operator": "GTE",
            "value": "2020-04-16T12:00:00.000Z"
        }
    ],
    "limit": "5"
}```
I get a `400 Bad request` response on this one. Is it possible that filters are just not working with dates?
